body:
A simple client-side mod supporting the Fabric, Forge, NeoForge, and Quilt mod loaders that removes all fog.  
&nbsp;  
&nbsp;  
There are no configs if [ClothConfig](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config) is not present. All fog will always remain disabled.  
&nbsp;  
Configs on Fabric/Quilt (1.16.5+):  
Configs can be changed from ingame if [ClothConfig](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config), [ModMenu](https://modrinth.com/mod/modmenu), and [FabricAPI](https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api)/[QSL](https://modrinth.com/mod/qsl) are present.

Configs on NeoForge (1.20.2+) & Forge (1.16.5 - 1.20.1):  
Configs can be changed from the main menu if [ClothConfig](https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config) is present.  
&nbsp;  
Configs can toggle each fog type when you are in biomes, dimensions, and globally in that order of priority.
